{"tid":228613,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋入lift見到一個好樣衰嘅男人會唔會覺得佢係色魔","createTime":"2017-05-04T04:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T07:12:39.000Z","uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b44acb6857094a284228b98f9295109a8373366","tid":228613,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"有一次搭lift準備關門<br />\n跟住有個靚女嗌等埋<br />\n我開返俾佢點知就睇到佢臉上流露不屑嘅眼神<br />\n睇得出佢有啲後悔入咗嚟<br />\n點知咁啱我哋又喺同一層落<br />\n出lift嗰陣佢好不安 係咁左顧右盼 可能覺得我係色魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次再遇到依個情況我應該點做？唔想俾人誤會我係死變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6715ae242bebfea4e0ddd0077d1a53bcaeccbc","tid":228613,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"除褲證明你無j"},{"pid":"80df0413eb6e29a4ac28ba304e7b12bb26b1a9b3","tid":228613,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"會啊"},{"pid":"c419ea088aeeb2158e0abfd079346b51fafab435","tid":228613,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會啊</blockquote><br />\n我係你啲屎"}]}